700025f-a.title: Bronx: 132nd Street (East) - St. Ann's Avenue
700025f-a.text:
595 East 132nd Street, east of the N.E. corner of St. Anns Ave.
The tracks, in the foreground, are of the New York, New Haven and Hartford
Railroad.
April 12, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
